<l>maruviṉ ṟokuti mayaṅkiyaṉ moḻiyu</l>
<l>muriyavai yuḷavē puṇarnilaic cuṭṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Words whose fusion<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">mayaṅku.</foreign></note> and accumulation<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">tokuti.</foreign></note></l>
<l>is sanctioned as <foreign xml:lang="ta">marūu</foreign><note place="foot">' contraction ', ' fusion ' of words resulting in metathesis authorized as grammatical e.g.<foreign xml:lang="ta"> il + muṉ &gt; muṉṟil</foreign> ' front-yard '.</note> do also occur</l>
<l>in the situation of juxtaposition.<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">puṇarnilai.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
